Get Deeper Insights from Survey Responses

Get the comprehensive Natural Language Processing Insights dashboard for a detailed analysis of survey results based on sentiments, extracted entities, and keyphrases. Use this analysis to assess trends and monitor frequently appearing keyphrases and entities in survey responses.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions of Feedback Management, where NLP Insights is enabled.

Who: The dashboards are a part of the Customer Lifecycle Analytics app and are available to users with the Salesforce Feedback Management license.

How: Enable NLP Insights, and then install the Customer Lifecycle Analytics app from Analytics Studio. To enable NLP insights, enter Industries AI Setup in the Quick Find box, select Industries AI Setup, and create a use case configuration for Entity and Keyphrase extraction.
title: Get Deeper Insights from Survey Responses with Salesforce
